title: Sappy Swifties Because Taylor's Songs Makes Our Tears Ricochet
description:
What Taylor Swift songs make you emotional? Or... what Taylor Swift songs doesn't make Ana emotional? Yeah. We will be here for a while!
Nick, Ana, Amy and Lacey share the songs that tug at their heart strings every single time!
What songs make you sappy, Swifties? And which ones did we forget to mention? Let us know!
